Lesson 13   A new dress

2
00:00:07,190 --> 00:00:13,760
Listen to the tape then answer this question.

3
00:00:13,760 --> 00:00:19,190
What colour is Anna's hat?

4
00:00:19,190 --> 00:00:23,910
What colour's your new dress?

5
00:00:23,910 --> 00:00:26,090
It's green.

6
00:00:26,090 --> 00:00:29,550
Come upstairs and see it.

7
00:00:29,550 --> 00:00:32,270
Thank you.

8
00:00:32,270 --> 00:00:33,820
Look!

9
00:00:33,820 --> 00:00:36,220
Here it is!

10
00:00:36,220 --> 00:00:38,910
That's a nice dress.

11
00:00:38,910 --> 00:00:42,490
It's very smart.

12
00:00:42,490 --> 00:00:46,160
My hat's new, too.

13
00:00:46,160 --> 00:00:49,760
What colour is it?

14
00:00:49,760 --> 00:00:52,380
It's the same colour.

15
00:00:52,380 --> 00:00:56,450
It's green, too.

16
00:00:56,450 --> 00:00:57,450
That is a lovely hat!
